    └── Custom → Raw Canvas/WebGL
```

### Comparison (2025)

| Framework | Type | Best For |
|-----------|------|----------|
| **Phaser 4** | 2D | Full game features |
| **PixiJS 8** | 2D | Rendering, UI |
| **Three.js** | 3D | Visualizations, lightweight |
